  # Volunteer in Denmark
  
  Are you a non-EU citizen wishing to be a volunteer in Denmark? You can find information below on the conditions to fulfil and procedures to follow, as well as the rights you can enjoy during your stay.
  
  - 1 April 2025
  
  ## Conditions
  
  For information on ‘Volunteers’, please visit the [official Portal for non-EU nationals who wish to visit, live or work in Denmark](https://www.nyidanmark.dk/en-GB/)
  
  ## Procedures
  
  For information on ‘Volunteers’, please visit the [official Portal for non-EU nationals who wish to visit, live or work in Denmark](https://www.nyidanmark.dk/en-GB/)
  
  ## Rights
  
  For information on ‘Volunteers’, please visit the [official Portal for non-EU nationals who wish to visit, live or work in Denmark](https://www.nyidanmark.dk/en-GB/)
  
