  ### Activity description
  
  DTU has a renewed focus on Diversity, Equity and Inclusion (DEI) and as such, parallel to the standard goings-on of the campus, DEI initiatives are integral to the wellbeing of students both on campus and at our student residences.
  
  Our Student’ Culture Hub team is one such initiative, and it is this team of which our four  ESC volunteers become a part. Student’s Culture Hub creates community building activities with the mission of creating inclusion and fostering belonging and combating loneliness on campus, and at our student residences. This is done through various activities, events and happenings that can range from cultural celebrations (Chinese New Year, Day of the Dead, Easter etc) to the fun-and-quirky (Cheese Rolling, Open Stage Jam, Drop-In DnD Night etc.).
  
